diff:1377878380:1377875883:=1c1,80%0a%3c Marked for Deletion%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a---%0a> http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/worldofdarknessmortal.png%0a> %0a> %25width=650px%25http://i.imgur.com/O1EWkKh.png%0a> -----%0a> '''%25purple%25Locations%25%25'''%0a> [[#Location]]%0a> *[[#Noble|Noble Fare]]%0a> *[[#Landing|The Landing]]%0a> *[[#SG|The Savannah Golf Club]]%0a> -----%0a> %0a> %0a> [[#Noble]]%0a> !!Noble Fare%0a> ''Jefferson and Harris''%0a> %0a> ''"Locally inspired cuisine with modern taste and historic charm"''%0a> %0a> Located in the heart of the Historic District, Noble Fair is an exclusive restaurant and wine bar. With expensive dishes, international wines and an intimate atmosphere, it serves as the meeting place of the elite.%0a> %0a> %25lfloat text-align=center margin-top=5px margin-right=15px margin-bottom=5px margin-left=0px%25http://i.imgur.com/V2yFCu4.jpg%0a> Within a renovated mansion converted into an intimate and high brow restaurant. The red brick exterior affords a cheery appearance, with a gracious wrought iron balcony and long white windows. The interior is intimate and painted in a dark crimson. Accented with black tables and chairs, the large dining hall is illuminated by candlelight and crystal chandeliers. The interior hums with the soft white noise of local chatter '-(Wits+Comp rolls suffer -1 penalty)-'. Upstairs, is the wine bar with its large selection of local and international wines. Dotted with small circular tables and framed by leather-bound booths.%0a> %0a> '''Cost:''' Resources 3+%0a> %0a> [[#Landing]]%0a> !!The Landings Club of Skidaway Island%0a> ''Skidaway Island''%0a> %0a> ''"It's day-to-day living flavored with a dash of vacation. It's unlimited recreation. It's outstanding service with attention to detail. It's peace and quiet available year round. The Landings Club offers a beautiful setting, a private playground, all for the exclusive enjoyment of Landings Club members and their guests."''%0a> %0a> Nestled quietly between the Wilmington River and Romerly Marsh, 12 miles southeast of Savannah, Georgia, The Landings Club is home to the serene natural beauty of majestic oaks and pines, lagoons and salt marshes, all complemented by world class amenities.%0a> %0a> %25lfloat text-align=center margin-top=5px margin-right=15px margin-bottom=5px margin-left=0px%25http://i.imgur.com/kqQtkNS.png%0a> Membership to the Landings Club affords access to one of the most exclusive and lavish amenities, dining and society that Savannah has to offer. Additionally, The Landings boasts 6 18-hole picturesque golf courses. From beautiful hardwood forests, marshes and tidal creeks, golfers enjoy the gorgeous sights of Mother Nature, while sinking a hole in one. Opulent, The Landing is more than a location, it’s a lifestyle.%0a> %0a> '''Memberships available:''' %0a> ->'''Social Membership'''- Grants members and their guests access to clubhouses, fitness and wellness center, swimming pools, dining and all social events and activities. Privileges extend to member, member’s spouse, and dependent children as prescribed by the Club.%0a> %0a> '''Costs:''' Resources 3 (Status High Society 2+, or allies High Society 2+)%0a> %0a> ->'''Tennis Membership'''- Exclusive access for members and their guests to tennis courts, clubhouses, fitness and wellness centers, swimming pools, dining and all social events and activities. Privileges extend to members, member’s spouse and dependent children as prescribed by the Club.%0a> %0a> '''Costs:''' Resources 4 (Status High Society 1+, or allies High Society 1+ and Status High Society 1+)%0a> %0a> ->'''Golf Membership'''- Grants members and their guests access to six championship golf courses, clubhouses, tennis courts, a fitness and wellness center, swimming pools, dining and all social events and activities. Privileges extend to member, member’s spouse, and dependent children as prescribed by the Club. Voting rights.%0a> %0a> '''Cost:''' Resources 4 (Status: High Society 2+, and allies High Society 1+)%0a> %0a> ''Membership to The Landings is entirely exclusive and dependent upon a characters standing within High Society, as well as any relevant skill or networks that they belong to, which appear favorable to the Club.''%0a> %0a> [[#SG]]%0a> !!The Savannah Golf Club%0a> ''E. President and Goebel''%0a> %0a> ''"The Savannah Golf Club is a private, member owned club which has existed to serve the social and recreational interests of its members since 1794."''%0a> %0a> The full service facility provides friendly and gracious service in an atmosphere conducive to good fellowship and camaraderie only found in exemplary Golf Country Clubs. %0a> %0a> %25lfloat text-align=center margin-top=5px margin-right=15px margin-bottom=5px margin-left=0px%25http://i.imgur.com/mFSclMY.jpg%0a> With offerings of golf, dining, tennis and swimming, The Savannah Golf Club is a membership based and member owned club located within West Chatham. Founded in 1796, it is the oldest Golf Club in America. With such a historical significance, there's no wonder why the older families gather here.%0a> %0a> '''Memberships available:''' %0a> ->'''Golf Membership'''- Grants members and immediate family full use of the Club facilities. Because this membership allows for golf privileges as well as voting rights, these memberships are limited.%0a> %0a> '''Costs:''' Resources 4 (Status High Society 2+, ond allies High Society 2+)%0a> %0a> ->'''Social Membership'''- Designed for members and immediate family who want access to Clubhouse activities, swimming, dining and tennis facilities of the Club. Social members do not have golfing privileges and may not golf, even as a guest.%0a> %0a> '''Costs:''' Resources 4 (Status High Society 2+, or Status High Society 1+ and allies High Society 2+)%0a> %0a> ->'''Junior Membership'''- Available to adults under the age of 36 and is available in both membership categories. This membership allows the member and immediate family members access to club facilities stipulated. Reduced monthly dues. No voting.%0a> %0a> '''Cost:''' Resources 3 (Status High Society 2+, or Status High Society 1+ and allies High Society 2+)%0a> %0a> ''By invitation only. Though inquiries can be sent to the Club. Sponsor required.''%0a> %0a> (:title Mortal Setting:)%0a> (:include GameRef.MortalRulesMaster#settingstart#settingend:)%0a> (:include CityBook.MortalNavigationBar:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
