diff:1377875883:1377849846:=3a4,7%0a> %0a> '''%25purple%25Playing Characters%25%25'''%0a> [[#NPC]]%0a> *[[#NF|Notable Faces]]%0a11a16,38%0a> %0a> [[#NF]]%0a> !!Notable Faces%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Paulina Potts''' (''Potts Family'') - As one of the Potts family that handles Blackwater Publishing and its various donations toward education and Bright Moon University, she appraises all incoming work and handles the fine editing once the staff has sorted out the worst offenses. A significant amount of her off-time is spent networking and reading to seek out the promising minds that Blackwater Publishing aids, and her opinion is of chief importance on the matter.'''- The youngest and is barely 2 0, though that doesn’t stop him from drinking in his father’s clubs. He’s known for his antics, which often are plastered across the gossip columns. He’s known for his excess and womanizing and at times can be seen attempting to fit in with harder, street affiliated friends.  %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' A pale woman about 5'9", with tangled black hair, wide glasses on a beaded string, and a somewhat mousey look. She wears conservative clothes with a slight eye for retro/vintage style qualities.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Academics, Crafts, Occult, Expression; rarely, initiation into (a yet-to-be-announced) Cult.%0a> %0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Albert Wainwright ''' (''Finance'') - Albert Wainwright isn't exactly a household name. He appears from time to time in a newspaper or a magazine due to his affluence and charity work, but few know more about him beyond that he comes from old money and manages it quite well with an exceedingly rich investment firm, Wainwright Capital Inc.%0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' An aging man that looks exceedingly healthy even for his 60's, with considerable height and wide shoulders. His hair is a bright gold peppered with white, slicked back impeccably with a feathery sort of edge at the back. His features are sharp and noble as if torn from royalty, and his bright hazel eyes stare forth with alarming acuity. He wears impeccable and wildly expensive attire, with preferences for gold highlights and avian motifs.%0a> %0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Politics, Expression, Intimidation, Persuasion. %0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Jessica Beaufort ''' (''Cosmetics'') -  A staple at every rally and a figure seen sparingly around town with public figures, Jessica is all smiles, sunshine, and every bit of sweetness nature can muster all wrapped into one person. She runs "Mother's Touch," a store exclusively selling organic makeup and body care products of varying prices to appeal to buyers of great and little wealth alike. She's a visible member of the Earth Heart Initiative ecoactivist group, almost always at the rallies but never making a big show of herself beyond occasional free samples. Regardless of where she is, she tends to pick out people who might need a cheering up or a burst of inspiration and applies her motherly charm and wisdom on a personal level.%0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' She's a tall black woman in her late 40's, but doesn't look her age. The image of youth shines through her sharp features, and she's always radiant. She dresses finely given her considerable wealth, but keeps everything she wears natural, especially her jewelry. She has a very bright and wide smile, though there is a slight glint in her gaze that suggests her smile could inspire as much fear as joy if she put her mind to it.%0a> %0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Politics, Persuasion, Socialize.%0a
