diff:1377849846:1377848593:=24a25,37%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Mariah Dawn Marie''' (''Fame 1 (80's icon), Song Producer, Record Label Owner'') -  At her height in the 1980's, Mariah-Dawn Marie was absolutely stunning. She possessed an easy aura of radiance that seemed to enhance her natural Americana features. She cultivated the role of the Southern belle, which was easily afforded due to the sweet and slow speech of her Savannah accent. But that was ages ago, now she offers a fair hand to local musicians, and in her thick Georgia accent she ensures that they know it's because she seeks preserve the South's place as a music powerhouse. It's rumored that she often doesn't take credit for the songs she crafts, and instead tells the recipients that the favor will one day be repaid in kind.  %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' Mariah-Dawn Marie appears physically as an older woman whose desperately grasping for the remnants of her youth. Often, she wears clothes that evoke the nostalgia of her previous incarnate as a pop singer in the 80's. Her face is tight, showing the abuse of facelifts and her lips sag in the corners from a habitual use of collagen injections. She seems frail, a touch distant but there's something uncanny about the sharpness in her green eyes.%0a> %0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Expression, Entertainment Connections, Media, Persuasion, Cult.%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Ernest Montgomery''' (''Business'') - The well known and public face to Ms. Marble's toy company, he's often seen in the eye of the media as a generous man in his 50's. A philanthropist, he donates copious amounts of dolls and money to local orphanages and even has a playground named after him. %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' Gray and a touch chubby, he wears classic suits with shiny black shoes. He's grandfatherly and moves with a slow-molasses like pace. He stands short at 5'5, and can even be seen in suspenders from time to time. He has a terrible cough, and often wheezes.%0a> %0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Business, philanthropy, Arts.%0a
