diff:1377848593:1377831696:=6a7,8%0a> *[[#Sterling|The Sterling Family]]%0a> *[[#Taylor|The Taylor Family]]%0a15c17,70%0a%3c %0a---%0a> [[#Sterling]]%0a> !!The Sterling Family%0a> %0a> ''"There's two things, only two things, that are certain in this world, and they're death and taxes. As a Sterling, our legacy is having forged that famous quote into a fiscal empire."'' %0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/crSoOTf.jpg '''Frances-Archibald Sterling'''- Frances-Archibald is the domineering patriarch of the Sterling lineage. He was born for the role of the patriarch, groomed throughout his entire life to ensure the success of his industry as well as his family. He's a man who maintains a physical and emotional distance from those he interact with, though, rumor says that he fell apart at the death of his eldest daughter, Eliza, some years ago. He's not a man eager to please, though, he does appreciate those that seek to curry his favor. %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' A coarse man within his late 50's, he has a domineering nature that exudes from the finer touches of his mannerisms. He carries himself with a great gravitas, a conditioning from the previous patriarchs who trained him for his role. Years in business has lent a dark and often times flat emotional bearing. %0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' High Society,Business, Allies/Contacts, City Contacts (Republican)%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/r3ELsAq.jpg'''Selene Sterling-Montgomery'''- Selene is socially aware and warm. She's accustomed to the small chit-chat of business, as well as the small social exchanges that pass by without word. She's active in in high society but has become less gaudy in her later years than she was previously. %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' Selene seems outwardly as a vain woman whose all too concerned with superficial necessities. Well groomed, impeccably dressed and thin, she carries an age old air of sophistication and a trained voice.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' High Society,%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/ot2NPm9.jpg'''Sebastian Sterling'''- Sebastian Sterling, the heir apparent is a man in his 30's whose returned to Georgia after nearly a decade away, presumably to assume his place as the leader of Sterling Industries. He's a man raised in country clubs and events, but seems entirely bored with it now. Rumors state that he was nearly a doctor before he returned back to the estate, an interesting pursuit given what the families main investments are. Frequently he's seen around town, rather than within the confines of the large family estate. Occasionally, he can be spotted at Good Samaritan Health Clinic.%0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' A handsome in a traditional, all-American way. Healthy, tall and fit with a dimpled chin, bright clear-blue eyes and his father's ash-blonde hair. He dresses in a conservative attempt of casual; button up collared shirts, slacks and the occasional sport coat. Additionally, he has soft written all over him; from his delicate touches, to how easily read his expressions are, he seems to not have inherited his fathers innate ability of maintaining distance and outward strength.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Medicine, Community Outreach.%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/1MuhhUz.jpg'''Patia Sterling'''- the youngest daughter of the Sterling line. Strangely, though her mother is active in socialite and high society events, Patia isn't. Instead, she is known as something of a recluse, oftentimes only being spotted at events that take place within her families estate and grounds. She's a pretty girl in her 20's, rumors at times are known to follow Patia, and the particularly vicious ones state that she's known to bounce in and out of mental health facilities and rehabilitation houses. %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' Long blonde hair and her mothers thin build, she would be pretty if it wasn't for a strange aura that surrounds her. Her movements are shy, introverted gestures accompanied by a nervous voice.%0a> %0a> [[#Taylor]]%0a> !!The Taylor Family%0a> ''"The Savannah I’m talking about, is a locally owned, locally ran Savannah; a modern Savannah that reflects its community."''%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/JO5kkLk.jpg'''William Taylor'''- William Taylor is a prominent and middle aged man who tries to use the gossip columns pre-occupation with his family to his advantage. He’s charismatic, boisterous and friendly, and given all the money he donates into local philanthropist organizations, he’s often seen in a saintly light. There’s rumors that his business practices are a whole lot less winsome, but often, these rumors are fought by the kinder stories of his community involvement, including the seminars he often runs. Personable, he’ll offer anyone a seat at his table, and is ingratiated into the culture of Savannah, oftentimes dining locally or having a drink at a local bar.%0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' A man in his laboring late 50's of a wide build. African- American and broad shouldered, standing at 6'4 with an impressive and boisterous laugh. He smells of cigars and vanilla aftershave and always wears a fashionable suit.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Academics, Business, Persuasion, Community Involvement.%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/ZH9qi2J.jpg'''Natasha Taylor'''- Natasha Taylor is William Taylor’s second wife, though his first, Connie, is rarely ever seen. Natasha, 30, is a failed model, a failed fashion designer and a failed interior designer, but she’s excelling at being social eye candy. She takes full advantage of the Taylor nightclubs and is known for her parties in equal measure to her fundraisers, Natasha, is a woman who’s almost always having an event. Rumor has it that Natasha’s trying to break into the upper echelons of Savannah society.%0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' An African-American woman in hear early 30's of a slender and tall build. She's 5'7, with delicate features and an overwhelming personality. Her clothes are always of the seasons fashion and she's often never seen with the same purse twice.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' High Society, Persuasion, Crafts, Presence, Contacts and Allies (Culture).%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/qZthuNG.jpg'''Trisha Taylor'''- Trisha Taylor is William’s oldest child and is a recent graduate of Savannah State University, in Journalism. She stays detached from her families affairs, though the media is prone to mentioning her in their society columns. She currently works for Savannah Morning News, and can be spotted around town sleuthing for stories. %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:''' A young African- American woman, 5'5, in her mid-twenties, she's pretty without being beautiful. Business casual is her game, along with a pair of sensible flats, often, she can be easily forgotten if it wasn't for the surname behind her first.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' Expression, Journalism and Sleuthing.%0a> %0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/L5hmCph.jpg'''Dwayne Taylor'''- The youngest and is barely 2 0, though that doesn’t stop him from drinking in his father’s clubs. He’s known for his antics, which often are plastered across the gossip columns. He’s known for his excess and womanizing and at times can be seen attempting to fit in with harder, street affiliated friends.  %0a> %0a> '''Physical Description:'''  A young African- American man barely over 20 in fashionable street styles and with a jovial, uplifting personality. He staggers sometimes as he walks, his gait unbalanced, though compensated with his theatrical hand motions. A height of 6'1 with a thin build.%0a> %0a> '''Available for Mentor teaching in:''' High Society,Party Culture, Streetwise, Various Contacts/Allies.%0a
