diff:1377829309:1377829231:=74,75c74,75%0a%3c %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Mariah Dawn Marie''' (''Fame 1 (80's icon), Song Producer, Record Label Owner'') -  At her height in the 1980's, Mariah-Dawn Marie was absolutely stunning. She possessed an easy aura of radiance that seemed to enhance her natural Americana features. She cultivated the role of the Southern belle, which was easily afforded due to the sweet and slow speech of her Savannah accent. But that was ages ago, now she offers a fair hand to local musicians, and in her thick Georgia accent she ensures that they know it's because she seeks preserve the South's place as a music powerhouse. It's rumored that she often doesn't take credit for the songs she crafts, and instead tells the recipients that the favor will one day be repaid in kind.  %0a%3c %0a---%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Mariah Dawn Marie'' (''Fame 1 (80's icon), Song Producer, Record Label Owner'') -  At her height in the 1980's, Mariah-Dawn Marie was absolutely stunning. She possessed an easy aura of radiance that seemed to enhance her natural Americana features. She cultivated the role of the Southern belle, which was easily afforded due to the sweet and slow speech of her Savannah accent. But that was ages ago, now she offers a fair hand to local musicians, and in her thick Georgia accent she ensures that they know it's because she seeks preserve the South's place as a music powerhouse. It's rumored that she often doesn't take credit for the songs she crafts, and instead tells the recipients that the favor will one day be repaid in kind.  %0a> %0a81,82c81,82%0a%3c %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Ernest Montgomery''' (''Business'') - The well known and public face to Ms. Marble's toy company, he's often seen in the eye of the media as a generous man in his 50's. A philanthropist, he donates copious amounts of dolls and money to local orphanages and even has a playground named after him. %0a%3c %0a---%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Ernest Montgomery'' (''Business'') - The well known and public face to Ms. Marble's toy company, he's often seen in the eye of the media as a generous man in his 50's. A philanthropist, he donates copious amounts of dolls and money to local orphanages and even has a playground named after him. %0a> %0a88,89c88,89%0a%3c %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Albert Wainwright ''' (''Finance'') - Albert Wainwright isn't exactly a household name. He appears from time to time in a newspaper or a magazine due to his affluence and charity work, but few know more about him beyond that he comes from old money and manages it quite well with an exceedingly rich investment firm, Wainwright Capital Inc.%0a%3c %0a---%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Albert Wainwright '' (''Finance'') - Albert Wainwright isn't exactly a household name. He appears from time to time in a newspaper or a magazine due to his affluence and charity work, but few know more about him beyond that he comes from old money and manages it quite well with an exceedingly rich investment firm, Wainwright Capital Inc.%0a> %0a95c95%0a%3c %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png'''Jessica Beaufort ''' (''Cosmetics'') -  A staple at every rally and a figure seen sparingly around town with public figures, Jessica is all smiles, sunshine, and every bit of sweetness nature can muster all wrapped into one person. She runs "Mother's Touch," a store exclusively selling organic makeup and body care products of varying prices to appeal to buyers of great and little wealth alike. She's a visible member of the Earth Heart Initiative ecoactivist group, almost always at the rallies but never making a big show of herself beyond occasional free samples. Regardless of where she is, she tends to pick out people who might need a cheering up or a burst of inspiration and applies her motherly charm and wisdom on a personal level.%0a---%0a> %25width=150px%25http://i.imgur.com/l6ksjmH.png''Jessica Beaufort '' (''Cosmetics'') -  A staple at every rally and a figure seen sparingly around town with public figures, Jessica is all smiles, sunshine, and every bit of sweetness nature can muster all wrapped into one person. She runs "Mother's Touch," a store exclusively selling organic makeup and body care products of varying prices to appeal to buyers of great and little wealth alike. She's a visible member of the Earth Heart Initiative ecoactivist group, almost always at the rallies but never making a big show of herself beyond occasional free samples. Regardless of where she is, she tends to pick out people who might need a cheering up or a burst of inspiration and applies her motherly charm and wisdom on a personal level.%0a
