diff:1377824267:1377823709:=30c30%0a%3c '''Physical Description:''' A handsome in a traditional, all-American way. Healthy, tall and fit with a dimpled chin, bright clear-blue eyes and his father's ash-blonde hair. He dresses in a conservative attempt of casual; button up collared shirts, slacks and the occasional sport coat. Additionally, he has soft written all over him; from his delicate touches, to how easily read his expressions are, he seems to not have inherited his fathers innate ability of maintaining distance and outward strength.%0a---%0a> '''Physical Description:''' A handsome man in an all-American way, he's blonde haired and blue eyed. Standing at 6'1 with a medium build and is often seen in casual khaki and collared shirts.%0a
